There will be a full inquiry.

1814
01:26:21.176 --> 01:26:22.886
[sobbing] No. no.

1815
01:26:22.969 --> 01:26:24.262
I'll give you a moment.

1816
01:26:26.723 --> 01:26:27.891
No...

1817
